title: Teemoing Issue
body: When I click the button to play, it doesn't sacrifice any minions and sits there.

replies.body: This issue might be caused by browser or extension issues getting in the way.  I recommend clearing your [cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies), running in Incognito, or trying another browser to fix this up.  Hope that helps!
